OL,3,CGolf club moving out of city and into
OL,4,Ccountryside
OL,6,FIt's more than 25 years since the idea
OL,7,Fwas first mooted, but Balmoral Golf
OL,8,FClub in Belfast has finally agreed to
OL,9,Fmove out of the city and into the
OL,10,Fcountryside.
OL,12,FA partnership deal with a Dublin
OL,13,Fproperty group to build a new 18-hole
OL,14,Fcourse and clubhouse in Drumbo a few
OL,15,Fmiles away has ended months of
OL,16,Ffinancial uncertainty for the cash-
OL,17,Fstrapped club and raises the potential
OL,18,Ffor new homes to be built on the
OL,19,FLisburn Road site.
