OL,6,FThe Balmoral course has long been
OL,7,Fassociated with the late, great golfer
OL,8,FFred Daly - the first Irishman to win
OL,9,Fthe British Open.
OL,11,FBut another golfing legend now has his
OL,12,Feye on the club's future.
OL,14,FFormer Ryder Cup Captain Paul McGinley
OL,15,Fhas designed the proposed course which
OL,16,Fis being built on the 149 acre New
OL,17,FGrove Estate at Ballylesson in Drumbo.
