OL,6,FHe paid a special visit to Belfast at
OL,7,Fthe weekend to show his plans to the
OL,8,FBalmoral golfers in their clubhouse at
OL,9,Fthe weekend.
OL,11,F"We're going to move just over three
OL,12,Fmiles from where we are now to a new
OL,13,Ffacility, a wonderful piece of land in
OL,14,Fmy view, to build a wonderful golf
OL,15,Fcourse," he said.
OL,17,FPlans to move from the current 75
OL,18,Facres site off Belfast's Lisburn Road
OL,19,Fhave met with resistance over the
OL,20,Fyears but an overwhelming majority now
OL,21,Fagree it's time to leave.
