OL,6,FVice-captain Bernie McNally said: "I
OL,7,Fthink now we're absolutely ready to
OL,8,Fmove because it's all about long term
OL,9,Fsustainability for the club, it's
OL,10,Fabout making sure we have a good
OL,11,Fstrong membership, it's about making
OL,12,Fsure we have a history and bring that
OL,13,Fhistory with us, but most important
OL,14,Fit's about the future."
OL,16,FThe partnership deal with the Merrion
OL,17,FProperty Group has saved the cash-
OL,18,Fstrapped club from the prospect of
OL,19,Fadministration.
