OL,6,FThe Dublin-based company will build
OL,7,Fthe new championship course and
OL,8,Fclubhouse and, subject to planning
OL,9,Fapproval, build new homes on the
OL,10,FBalmoral site when it becomes vacant.
OL,12,FIf all goes to plan, Balmoral Golf
OL,13,FClub will relocate to its new home in
OL,14,Fthree to five years time - ready for
OL,15,Fthe next generation of players to tee
OL,16,Foff.
